    {
        "content": "<p>Fixed patch links:</p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://android-review.googlesource.com/c/kernel/common/+/2930614\">2930614: ANDROID: rust: Support arrays in target JSON</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://android-review.googlesource.com/c/kernel/common/+/2930615\">2930615: ANDROID: rust: Use From instances for JSON encoder</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://android-review.googlesource.com/c/kernel/common/+/2930616\">2930616: ANDROID: rust: Enable KCFI support when available</a></li>\n</ul>",
